{"id":"5e9c05cf774c2610387e4deb","title":"Artist Profile: Arvor","content":"<p>Sometimes we forget that photojournalism isn’t just paparazzi waiting outside hotels to catch celebrities in compromising situations.</p><p>  <b>Arvor</b> is a collective of 40 Press and Editorial graduates from <b>Falmouth University</b>. The photographs exhibited are painfully realistic  shots of poignant contemporary issues, rigorously researched, that might have otherwise escaped our attention. From uncovering a lesser-known Amish community in Ireland, to delving into the psychology of musical tribute acts, all investigations are dealt with respect, tact and elegance.</p>\n<p><b>Arvor</b> will be holding a summer festival to exhibit their work in Falmouth until the 23<sup>rd</sup> June.</p>\n<p>For those who aren’t in the West Country, check out each photographers stunning portfolio on their website <a href=\"https://arvor.weservesites.co.uk/\">HERE</a>.</p>\n<p>..and some examples below.</p>\n\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t\t#gallery-7 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-7 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 25%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-7 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-7 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-7' class='gallery galleryid-22466 gallery-columns-4 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://localhost:8888/arts/22466-artist-profile-arvor/attachment/kosovo-forgotten-but-not-gone'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://localhost:8888/uploads/2013/06/Alexander-Walker-150x150.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/images/2013/06/Alexander-Walker-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://api.crackintheroad.co